  "detailed_description": "All the same, all the time. Day in, day out. But maybe there is more, if you just look close enough ... and remember.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recollect your surroundings</h2>Bring the forgotten wonders of this beautiful world back to your attention.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Varied gameplay</h2>Rediscover fascinating things like the stars, flowers and trees in playful experiences.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Two game modes</h2>Face the many threats these wonders are facing in the optional second \"fragile mode\".<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2>Adjust the game to your likings through many settings, i.e. change the difficulty seamlessly at any time without getting punished for it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Many wonderful things to discover in hand-crafted, diverse experiences<br></li><li> Casual, accessible gameplay<br></li><li> Two game modes: Natural (relaxed & wholesome) / Fragile (challenging & concerning)<br></li><li> Atmospheric silhouette artstyle<br></li><li> Emotional, magical soundtrack<br></li><li> Short playtime of about 1-2 hours<br></li><li> Playable with mouse & keyboard, controller or just using the mouse</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "All the same, all the time. Day in, day out. But maybe there is more, if you just look close enough ... and remember.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recollect your surroundings</h2>Bring the forgotten wonders of this beautiful world back to your attention.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/970935a65a00615b55dff88ef7d004eb.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Varied gameplay</h2>Rediscover fascinating things like the stars, flowers and trees in playful experiences.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/50f39c49a49820fc71e7059343d037ea.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Two game modes</h2>Face the many threats these wonders are facing in the optional second \"fragile mode\".<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/d8dfd3cccb09f0d1245a530cb3796e36.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessibility</h2>Adjust the game to your likings through many settings, i.e. change the difficulty seamlessly at any time without getting punished for it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.poster.avif?t=1764665192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.webm?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1804610/extras/3b3058bee58a53c2d18083c00fda410c.mp4?t=1764665192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Many wonderful things to discover in hand-crafted, diverse experiences<br></li><li> Casual, accessible gameplay<br></li><li> Two game modes: Natural (relaxed & wholesome) / Fragile (challenging & concerning)<br></li><li> Atmospheric silhouette artstyle<br></li><li> Emotional, magical soundtrack<br></li><li> Short playtime of about 1-2 hours<br></li><li> Playable with mouse & keyboard, controller or just using the mouse</li></ul>",
